咪口乾鼻乾同眼瞓。但安眠作用唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3c82335643bb6ba2803c0b896566d49e69d8ca","tid":276434,"uid":87644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T22:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爬過文 有隻安眠藥叫第一代抗組織胺（Antihistamine）例如chlorpheniramine或promethazine<br />\n藥房買到<br />\n有冇巴絲試過有冇副作用or其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲好安全 有啲人比bb仔食想佢地瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4b623a1e7b6286e08365e932d5908d0016e0d0","tid":276434,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T22:52:21.000Z","msg":"算啦醒起啲嘢 當我冇問過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cebbcb1e1c5279e2b8072f44cd36ca3e3bc1921","tid":276434,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T23:55:29.000Z","msg":"piriton <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ba7a8bd73e270ef8d6d67841e4e824c759f184","tid":276434,"uid":106126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爬過文 有隻安眠藥叫第一代抗組織胺（Antihistamine）例如chlorpheniramine或promethazine<br />\n藥房買到<br />\n有冇巴絲試過有冇副作用or其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得好有用"},{"pid":"cc962bb2a11e40aaf22b02043ae8691930e14d62","tid":276434,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食放鬆神經藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e14024ab7c773de6a8ff2e41bc0eba7504dc33","tid":276434,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:27:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8935adf575b4fd329e01e4587b9dd15134de1397","tid":276434,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"褪黑激素"},{"pid":"af377a0eea7a704d703e308aa1eee6728dcae49e","tid":276434,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>爬過文 有隻安眠藥叫第一代抗組織胺（Antihistamine）例如chlorpheniramine或promethazine<br />\n藥房買到<br />\n有冇巴絲試過有冇副作用or其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得好有用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美研究：長期服過敏藥恐提高失智風險<br />\n2016/04/19 18:24<br />\n<br />\n美國最新研究指出，長期服用抗過敏藥、抗花粉熱藥及安眠藥等藥物，時間達3年以上，可能損害認知能力，也提高罹患失智症的風險。<br />\n<br />\n研究中所提到的藥物是抗膽鹼能藥（anticholinergic drugs），美國印第安納大學醫學院（Indiana University School of Medicine）學者讓451名平均73歲的銀髮族做記憶與認知測驗，並用核磁共振（MRI）掃瞄腦部，利用正子電腦斷層掃描（PET）測量腦部的新陳代謝功能。結果發現，使用抗膽鹼能藥的60名受測者在認知及短期記憶測驗的表現，低於未服用藥物的老人，用藥者也有早期失智症的病徵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160419/842453/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20160419%2F842453%2F&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ce053c0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160419/842453/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCommon anticholinergic drugs like Benadryl linked to increased dementia risk<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.health.harvard.edu/blog/common-anticholinergic-drugs-like-benadryl-linked-increased-dementia-risk-201501287667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fblog%2Fcommon-anticholinergic-drugs-like-benadryl-linked-increased-dementia-risk-201501287667&d=ayWF0Xl6EeUFaLntekyQBtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=47e00105\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.health.harvard.edu/blog/common-anticholinergic-drugs-like-benadryl-linked-increased-dementia-risk-201501287667</a>"},{"pid":"916729593ed203172c1459d370c55c559bd79ac4","tid":276434,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"抗組織胺係收鼻水藥，副作用係眼訓<br />\n但副作用生效時間遲，而且長<br />\n<br />\n真係想食訓覺藥就應該食stilnox<br />\n再勁d食zolpiclone<br />\n再勁就係藍睛靈 乜乜zolum"},{"pid":"f5c0a7dffed28ad58819182fccf9b3494abd7153","tid":276434,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"食感冒藥"},{"pid":"949dd7d72ae815710b97c3edf01081af0089d54e","tid":276434,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抗組織胺係收鼻水藥，副作用係眼訓<br />\n但副作用生效時間遲，而且長<br />\n<br />\n真係想食訓覺藥就應該食stilnox<br />\n再勁d食zolpiclone<br />\n再勁就係藍睛靈 乜乜zolum</blockquote><br />\n梗係用zolpidem"}]}